---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">About Me</h1>
    
    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      Hi, I’m <strong>Redžo Efendić</strong> 👋 — a web developer passionate about 
      JavaScript, Node.js, React, and building modern web applications. 
      Over the past two years, I’ve worked on various projects ranging from backend APIs 
      to interactive frontend applications, always aiming to create clean, 
      user-friendly, and practical solutions.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">💼 Work Experience</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Encode IT Education & Mentorship</strong> — Completed intensive training with mentors, building real-world projects using JavaScript, Node.js, Express, MongoDB and React.</li>
      <li><strong>ZeForge Zenica Community</strong> — Collaborated on an app related to public transport and website for the mountain Smetovi near Zenica, Bosnia and Herzegovina, gaining teamwork and project experience in a real community setting.</li>
      <li><strong>Personal Projects</strong> — Developed multiple applications including <em>My Portfolio Website</em> and <em>Prayer Time App</em>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">🎓 Education</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
      <li>IT Education at <strong>Encode</strong> — Hands-on learning with guidance from experienced mentors.</li>
      <li>Continuous self-learning — Strengthened my skills by building projects and exploring new technologies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">🛠️ Skills</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">Here are the technologies I use most often:</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">JavaScript</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">Node.js</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">Express</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">MongoDB</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">React</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">Astro</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">HTML</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">CSS</span>
      <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full">Git & GitHub</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4">🌍 Beyond Code</h2>
    <p class="leading-relaxed">
      In addition to coding, I enjoy teaching others and sharing knowledge. 
      I’ve prepared lessons for my students and created educational 
      presentations. Helping others learn motivates me to keep growing as a developer 
      and as a teacher.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
